<a href="/questions/1439420-oh-my-friend-now-she-s-not-puerto-rican">Oh my friend, Now she&#39;s not Puerto Rican because &quot;the time is over&quot;.
Does she know what &quot;I was&quot; mean? Very easy dear Watson. Better 
&quot;when I lived in Puerto Rico&quot; or &quot;When I grew up in Puerto Rico&quot;.
dear Watson.</a>
