        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2400005747" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16651559488956527520">This isn&apos;t a full review, because I read this when it published so many years ago, but I do remember finishing it with a new appreciation for all that my parents went through when they moved from Puerto Rico to New York. A great book that I highly recommend.</span>
  <span id="freeText16651559488956527520" style="display:none">This isn't a full review, because I read this when it published so many years ago, but I do remember finishing it with a new appreciation for all that my parents went through when they moved from Puerto Rico to New York. A great book that I highly recommend.</span>
