<div id="review_2235153237" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2235153237" />
    <a title="Theresa Connors" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1281056-theresa-connors"><img alt="Theresa Connors" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1443308318p2/1281056.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2235153237?book_show_action=true">Dec 31, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Theresa Connors" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Theresa Connors" href="/user/show/1281056-theresa-connors">Theresa Connors</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/34875647-when-i-was-puerto-rican">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2235153237" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6359556112306716113">Santiago’s lyrical memoir, the first volume of a trilogy, focuses on her childhood in Puerto Rico. She immigrated to New York with her five siblings and mother in the early 60s. As her family grew to eleven children, she excelled in school in spite of poverty and limited English proficiency. She beat the odds and was accepted into the School of Performing Arts in Manhattan, going on to graduate from Harvard. She’s an exceptional storyteller-this reads like nicely crafted novel. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

